* Support nested not-required options:

  command [ --foo=$foo [ --bar=$bar ] ]

* Support optional arguments (an argument can be or not given for some
  option):

  command --foo=[$foo]

* Support mutual exclusive options (only one can be given):

  command --foo | --bar
* Support float ranges
* Support testing not giving any argument to some parameter that
  requires an argument: 'command --set-hour '.
* Explain terminology used (e.g. option, argument, ...) and ensure that
  the terms are used consistently through the code and documentation.
* Support validating positional parameters.
